हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Supreme Lord” is a dark love story where two souls struggle to protect their bond against the forces of evil. Even as fear and destruction consume the world, their love stands as the only light strong enough to defy the darkness.
